Class AbstractOrderedDiffTreeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.diff.node.AbstractOrderedDiffTreeNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDiffTreeNode<AbstractOrderedDiffTreeNode>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractDiffItemDiffTreeNode, TextDiffTreeNode

    public abstract class AbstractOrderedDiffTreeNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDiffTreeNode<AbstractOrderedDiffTreeNode>
    An implementation of IDiffTreeNode that orders its children based on the getSortOrder() and then getLabel() properties.
